-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Download and install GCC GNU Compiler

2. clone the repo 
   git clone https://github.com/UsboKirishima/PizzaPastaMandolin/
   cd PizzaPastaMandolin
   
3. Compile and run! bash
   gcc main.c cli_colors.c integration.c -o main
   ./main

